(239, 21, '17:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 30, 'Special Lecture', 'Finggal Link Co., Ltd. (フィンガルリンク株式会社)/Honda Electronics Co., Ltd. (本多電子株式会社)', 'Distal Radial Artery Approach (SnuffBox Radial Approach: SBRA)', 'HAMAGIN Hall', 'Distal radial artery approach is getting more and more popular also in JAPAN. This artery is called "SnuffBox artery" or "princeps pollicis artery". Dr. Kiemeneij is one of the pioneers in this field. He will talk about the pitfalls, advantages and disadvantages of this SnuffBox Radial Approach (SBRA) or princeps pollicis artery procedure (PPAP). You have to join this session in order to keep updates of TRI.', '2018-09-02 12:00:00', 'tri', 2017, '2017-12-09'),
